{"tid":1766452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[打氣區!] 仲有三星期就聖誕, 離裁員潮不遠矣","createTime":"2019-12-02T14:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T16:21:54.000Z","uid":155883,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b3d2a9e07cb638cc40e05d22744f3e022d5f4254","tid":1766452,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:55:44.000Z","msg":"提下大家, 仲有三星期就聖誕, 元旦<br />\n七星期後就新年, 只有大節時市道蕭條就係勝利既徵兆<br />\n十月零售指數跌左24.3%根本有水份<br />\n1/10 - 7/10 全香港根本冇做過生意<br />\n8號開始玩宵禁, 黨鐵 8點收車, 而且好多個站都封左<br />\n6點後基本上冇夜生活, 由其retail, 餐飲<br />\n之後大部分時間都係9點10點收車<br />\n香港人慢慢都冇哂夜生活<br />\n奢侈品就唔洗講, 大環境係大陸經濟都唔好<br />\nrmb 對港冇以前咁抵<br />\n而且落黎買貴野都非富則貴<br />\n命仔重要, 點會落黎搏<br />\n24% 一定有水份<br />\n但anyway 11月一定30%+ <br />\n我希望12月可以上到 40%<br />\n同意既幫手推"},{"pid":"9979e9ad54264810139358364ad83d81aa9edd52","tid":1766452,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:02:36.000Z","msg":"推下!!!"},{"pid":"e5d2ac07545122ca6001a0dd6abf7a571d3dd468","tid":1766452,"uid":171849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb0ac4b740784dfc73d9382a98deb122685c4bd","tid":1766452,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:08:26.000Z","msg":"認真POST, 入黎打下氣先啦"},{"pid":"e9693ccffe2085f405cc3f3cfb81fb33b7b0b581","tid":1766452,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T16:21:54.000Z","msg":"推"}]}